text: Noordsebuurt is a village in the Dutch province of South Holland. It is a part of the municipality of Nieuwkoop, and lies about 10 km north of Woerden. The statistical area "Noordsebuurt", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 210.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005.
